name: io.bytes.per.checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  io.file.buffer.size.

name: dfs.namenode.delegation.token.renew-interval
description: The renewal interval for delegation token in milliseconds.

name: dfs.client.deadnode.detection.probe.connection.timeout.ms
description: Connection timeout for probing dead node in milliseconds.

name: tfile.fs.input.buffer.size
description: Buffer size used for FSDataInputStream in bytes.

name: dfs.client.test.drop.namenode.response.number
description:
The number of Namenode responses dropped by DFSClient for each RPC call.  Used
    for testing the NN retry cache.
